2.1.3. A postal address;
2.1.4. Your phone number;
2.1.5. Details on your cars;
2.1.6. Your mini-biography, possible preferences and hobbies when you agree to provide that information;
2.1.7. A record of any bookings you have made with our platform;
2.1.8. Details of accounting or financial transactions including transactions carried out through our platform or otherwise. This may include information such as your payment card or bank account details, details of trips you have booked through our platform;
